(1114, 1, '2015-04-09 08:24:02', '2015-04-09 08:24:02', 'Jaina Proudmoore is a master spellcaster, trained by the legendary Archmage Antonidas himself. Brilliant, courageous, and wise, it was Jaina who led the survivors of the Scourge of Lordaeron to safety. But don''t mistake her graciousness for weakness, or she will gladly demonstrate to you the folly of picking a fight with a sorceress.', 'Jaina Proudmoore', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'jaina-proudmoore', '', '', '2015-04-13 14:55:55', '2015-04-13 14:55:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webgame/?post_type=fl_champion&#038;p=1114', 0, 'fl_champion', '', 0),
(1115, 1, '2015-04-09 08:22:11', '2015-04-09 08:22:11', 'The Lost Vikings are back! While they briefly considered retirement after defeating the emperor Tomator, there were only so many polar bears they could wrestle before falling into a Nexus portal seemed like a solid life decision.', 'The Lost Vikings', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-lost-vikings', '', '', '2015-04-13 09:16:36', '2015-04-13 09:16:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webgame/?post_type=fl_champion&#038;p=1115', 0, 'fl_champion', '', 0),
(1116, 1, '2015-04-09 08:24:08', '2015-04-09 08:24:08', '<p>Jaina Proudmoore is a master spellcaster, trained by the legendary Archmage Antonidas himself. Brilliant, courageous, and wise, it was Jaina who led the survivors of the Scourge of Lordaeron to safety. But don''t mistake her graciousness for weakness, or she will gladly demonstrate to you the folly of picking a fight with a sorceress.</p>\n', 'Jaina Proudmoore', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1114-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-04-09 08:24:08', '2015-04-09 08:24:08', '', 1114, 'http://localhost/webgame/?p=1116', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
